data.description: This stunning renovated single family home features three ample bedrooms, a beautifully updated kitchen, updated bathrooms, newer roof (2019) and a versatile floor plan making it ideal for family living and entertaining! This home also has a newer HVAC (2019), cozy sun room, gorgeous new bamboo flooring, new attic insulation, solar panels, electric vehicle charger plus an oversized driveway. Turnkey ready for its new owners. Conveniently located for shopping and interstate travel. Oh and it's 1 block from the water! Schedule your viewing today!
